DBsheetConfig.query: SELECT T1.Id, T1.GroupingId, T4.value Calendar, T5.value LongFixedFrequency, T6.value LongFixedConvention, T7.value LongFixedDayCounter, T8.value LongIndex, T9.value ShortFixedFrequency, T10.value ShortFixedConvention, T11.value ShortFixedDayCounter, T12.value ShortIndex, T13.value LongMinusShort FROM ORE.dbo.ConventionsTenorBasisTwoSwap T1 LEFT JOIN ORE.dbo.TypesCalendar T4 ON T1.Calendar = T4.value LEFT JOIN ORE.dbo.TypesFrequencyType T5 ON T1.LongFixedFrequency = T5.value LEFT JOIN ORE.dbo.TypesBusinessDayConvention T6 ON T1.LongFixedConvention = T6.value LEFT JOIN ORE.dbo.TypesDayCounter T7 ON T1.LongFixedDayCounter = T7.value LEFT JOIN ORE.dbo.TypesIndexName T8 ON T1.LongIndex = T8.value LEFT JOIN ORE.dbo.TypesFrequencyType T9 ON T1.ShortFixedFrequency = T9.value LEFT JOIN ORE.dbo.TypesBusinessDayConvention T10 ON T1.ShortFixedConvention = T10.value LEFT JOIN ORE.dbo.TypesDayCounter T11 ON T1.ShortFixedDayCounter = T11.value LEFT JOIN ORE.dbo.TypesIndexName T12 ON T1.ShortIndex = T12.value LEFT JOIN ORE.dbo.TypesBool T13 ON T1.LongMinusShort = T13.value

field.name: *Calendar
field.lookup: SELECT !T!.value Calendar, !T!.value FROM ORE.dbo.TypesCalendar !T! ORDER BY value

field.name: *LongFixedFrequency
field.lookup: SELECT !T!.value LongFixedFrequency, !T!.value FROM ORE.dbo.TypesFrequencyType !T! ORDER BY value

field.name: *LongFixedConvention
field.lookup: SELECT !T!.value LongFixedConvention,!T!.value FROM ORE.dbo.TypesBusinessDayConvention !T! ORDER BY value

field.name: *LongFixedDayCounter
field.lookup: SELECT !T!.value LongFixedDayCounter, !T!.value FROM ORE.dbo.TypesDayCounter !T! ORDER BY value

field.name: *LongIndex
field.lookup: SELECT !T!.value LongIndex,!T!.value FROM ORE.dbo.TypesIndexName !T! ORDER BY value

field.name: *ShortFixedFrequency
field.lookup: SELECT !T!.value ShortFixedFrequency, !T!.value FROM ORE.dbo.TypesFrequencyType !T! ORDER BY value

field.name: *ShortFixedConvention
field.lookup: SELECT !T!.value ShortFixedConvention,!T!.value FROM ORE.dbo.TypesBusinessDayConvention !T! ORDER BY value

field.name: *ShortFixedDayCounter
field.lookup: SELECT !T!.value ShortFixedDayCounter, !T!.value FROM ORE.dbo.TypesDayCounter !T! ORDER BY value

field.name: *ShortIndex
field.lookup: SELECT !T!.value ShortIndex,!T!.value FROM ORE.dbo.TypesIndexName !T! ORDER BY value

field.name: LongMinusShort
field.lookup: SELECT !T!.value LongMinusShort,!T!.value FROM ORE.dbo.TypesBool !T! ORDER BY value
